---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Community Development">
  <div class="container" style="padding: var(--spacing-6) 0;">
    
    <nav aria-label="Breadcrumbs" style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4);">
      <a href="/">Home</a> &gt; <a href="/programs/">Programs</a> &gt; <span aria-current="page">Community Development</span>
    </nav>
    <header style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-6);">
      <h1 style="font-size: 2.5rem; color: var(--color-primary-blue);">Community Development</h1>
      <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--color-text-muted);">Empowering our community via outreach, mentoring, and collaborative development initiatives.</p>
    </header>
    <div class="grid" style="grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr; gap: var(--spacing-6);">
      <div class="main-content">
        <section style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-5);">
          <h2>What the Service Is</h2>
          <p>Our community development initiative bridges the gap between individuals and opportunities. We offer financial literacy programming, food and nutrition planning, job preparation, and cultural interest activities that uplift the underserved in Baltimore.</p>
        </section>
        <section style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-5);">
          <h2>Who It Is For</h2>
          <p>All members of the Baltimore community who are seeking enrichment, mentorship, access to essential commodities, or guidance on establishing stable living environments.</p>
        </section>
        <section style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-5);">
          <h2>How to Qualify</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Various elements of the community program are widely open; specific workshops may require a brief registration.</li>
            <li>Priority access for existing WEL Foundation clients.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>
        <section style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-5);">
          <h2>What Happens Next</h2>
          <p>Community members can reach out via the contact form to express interest. For directed mentorship, submit an intake form and our staff will respond within <strong>3 business days</strong> with placement resources.</p>
        </section>
      </div>
      <aside>
        <div class="card" style="background-color: var(--color-bg-offset); border-top: 4px solid var(--color-accent-gold);">
          <h3>Take the First Step</h3>
          <a href="/contact/" class="btn" style="display: block; width: 100%; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2);">Contact the Team</a>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
